</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
General Manager Tom Flores and owner Ken Behring of the Seattle Seahawks have 
been served with subpoenas in connection with the California murder charge 
against former team official Mike Blatt. 
</P>
<P>
"I was kind of surprised (about the subpoena) because of the fact that the only 
